        <mxCell id="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-82" parent="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-28" style="swimlane;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#b85450;fillColor=#f8cecc;startSize=23;" value="Treinamento" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="300" x="410" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-84" parent="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-82" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;KNN&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;metric=&#39;manhattan&#39;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;n_neighbors=11&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Acurácia: 83%&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="180" x="60" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-83" edge="1" parent="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-85" source="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-82" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);" target="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-26">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-86" parent="3f-skZgC5im7CZNcT9Cw-1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#EAEDED,#F7F7F7);fontSize=22;fontColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=none;labelBackgroundColor=none;arcSize=8;shadow=1;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="355" x="347" y="-440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bdhlae-sQzXAQDbLg7Tm-87" parent="3f-skZgC5im7CZNcT9Cw-1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Processo de treinamento&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;O dataset escolhido foi o Employee disponível no&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font&gt;kaggle&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;Foi necessário converter os campos&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;Education, City, Gender, EverBenched que contém dados categóricos em números e armazenar os rótulos em um dicionário para uso posterior&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Foi aplicada a separação de 20% para dados de teste&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Foram avaliados os algoritmos KNN, CART, NB e SVN sem padronização e normalização e o CART atingiu 81% de acurácia, entretanto após a padronização e normalização o SVN padronizado atingiu 83%&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Foi feito um fine tuning para SVN e KNN.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Na fase de treino o SVN se mostrou promissor, entretanto em produção o KNN se mostrou mais eficiente na avaliações.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;O modelo foi exportado utilizando pickle&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="265" width="320" x="367" y="-435" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
